      <title>三菱日联金融集团员工因涉嫌泄露内幕信息接受调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/mufg-bank-employee-probed-for-suspected-inside-information-leak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本媒体报道称，三菱日联银行一名员工涉嫌向家人泄露要约收购细节及其他有关客户公司的非公开信息。数周前，该银行集团因突破防火墙而受到谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/mufg-bank-employee-probed-for-suspected-inside-information-leak</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 00:12:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
